						<li>Use the app to create unlawful, defamatory, harassing, hateful, or fraudulent content.</li>
						<li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or extract source code from the app.</li>
						<li>Circumvent usage limits, quotas, or subscription restrictions.</li>
						<li>Use automated scripts or bots to access the service outside official APIs.</li>
						<li>Generate synthetic media depicting a real, identifiable person without their explicit consent.</li>
						<li>Interfere with the security or operation of the app or our servers.</li>
					</ul>
					<p>We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate these rules.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
