					<p>{APP_NAME}, its logo, software, prompts, models, and platform assets are the intellectual property of {DEVELOPER_NAME}. These Terms do not transfer any ownership of the app to you.</p>

					<h3>6.3 AI-generated effects</h3>
					<p>Visual and sound effects generated by AI are provided for use in your edits. You are responsible for reviewing outputs before publishing and ensuring your use does not infringe third-party rights. We do not warrant that AI outputs are original, error-free, or eligible for copyright protection.</p>

					<h3>6.4 Copyright complaints</h3>
					<p>If you believe content processed through the app infringes your copyright, contact <a href="mailto:support@thinkingcats.com">support@thinkingcats.com</a> with a description of the work, the infringing material, and your contact information. We will respond to valid notices as required by law.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>7. AI Features Disclaimer</h2>
					<p>AI analysis and generation may produce inaccurate, incomplete, or unexpected results. Outputs are provided <strong>as is</strong> without warranties of accuracy, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement. You are solely responsible for content you export and publish.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
